// Ragnarok - a renegade Terran warlord. When the raiders thin out, the "42 Fleet"
// warps in: the juggernaut Ragnarok, the light cruiser XORN, and renegade escorts.
// Beat Ragnarok to win - or turn XORN (a //comms appeal in siege.mast), who then
// rounds on Ragnarok. Authored in the shared AMD quest vocabulary.

# [Ragnarok](ragnarok)
---
Trigger: enemies_low
Low: 30%
Flies: pirate
Fleets: 3
Difficulty: +2
Named: Ragnarok tsn_juggernaut, XORN tsn_light_cruiser
---
The 42 Fleet warps in under the renegade Admiral Ragnarok - a Terran juggernaut and its honor guard.

## [Defeat Ragnarok](defeat_ragnarok)
---
Scope: shared
State: active
Parent: siege_mission
Required: true
Goal: destroy 1 ragnarok
When: signal siege_won
Pays: 800 credits
---
Destroy the juggernaut Ragnarok to break the 42 Fleet.

## [Turn Xorn](turn_xorn)
---
Scope: shared
State: active
Parent: siege_mission
When: signal xorn_defected
Pays: 400 credits
---
Hail the light cruiser XORN and appeal to their honor - convince them to turn on Ragnarok.
